4. npx nodemon index.js ## nodemon 

ğŸ§ª API Endpoints


| Method | Endpoint         | Description       |
| ------ | ---------------- | ----------------- |
| GET    | `/api/items`     | Get all items     |
| GET    | `/api/items/:id` | Get item by ID    |
| POST   | `/api/items`     | Create a new item |
| DELETE  | `/api/items`     | Delete an item by using id |

